'''新井凉平'''（{{jpn|j=新井 涼平|hg=あらい りょうへい|rm=Arai Ryōhei}}，{{bd|1991年|6月23日||}}）生于埼玉县，是一名日本男子田径运动员，主攻标枪。他在小学时接触过[[垒球|垒球]]，中学时则练习[[棒球|棒球]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympicchannel.com/ja/stories/features/detail/%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%95%E6%B6%BC%E5%B9%B3-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%99%B8%E4%B8%8A%E3%81%AB%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E3%81%95%E3%82%8C%E3%82%84%E3%82%8A%E6%8A%95%E3%81%91%E3%81%AE%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%81%AB-%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E3%81%A62%E5%BA%A6%E7%9B%AE%E3%81%AE%E4%BA%94%E8%BC%AA%E5%87%BA%E5%A0%B4%E3%82%92%E7%9B%AE%E6%8C%87%E3%81%99/|script-title=ja:新井涼平：世界陸上に影響されやり投げの世界に...東京で2度目の五輪出場を目指す|publisher=[[奥林匹克频道|Olympic Channel]]|date=2019-03-28|accessdate=2020-09-16|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200916072836/https://www.olympicchannel.com/ja/stories/features/detail/%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%95%E6%B6%BC%E5%B9%B3-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%99%B8%E4%B8%8A%E3%81%AB%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E3%81%95%E3%82%8C%E3%82%84%E3%82%8A%E6%8A%95%E3%81%91%E3%81%AE%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%81%AB-%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E3%81%A62%E5%BA%A6%E7%9B%AE%E3%81%AE%E4%BA%94%E8%BC%AA%E5%87%BA%E5%A0%B4%E3%82%92%E7%9B%AE%E6%8C%87%E3%81%99/|archivedate=2020-09-16}}</ref>。2007年，他在电视上观看芬兰标枪选手[[泰罗·皮特凯迈基|泰罗·皮特凯迈基]]比赛后，决定于高中一年级第二学期时加入田径部，转攻标枪<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.incheon2014ag.org/Sports/Biographies/Athletes_Profile/?ParticCode=5103341&lang=en|title=Ryohei Arai|work=Incheon 2014|accessdate=2020-09-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007012106/http://www.incheon2014ag.org/Sports/Biographies/Athletes_Profile/?ParticCode=5103341&lang=en|archivedate=2014-10-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://sports.yahoo.co.jp/column/detail/201409080008-spnavi?page=1|script-title=ja:やり投げの新星・新井涼平、覚醒の理由 「記録を狙える」アジア大会への自信|publisher=Sportsnavi|date=2014-09-08|accessdate=2020-09-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917005739/https://sports.yahoo.co.jp/column/detail/201409080008-spnavi?page=1|archivedate=2020-09-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年至2014年间，他就读于国士馆大学体育学部<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kokushikan.ac.jp/tokyo2020/olympian.html|script-title=ja:国士舘のオリンピアン|work={{lang|ja|国士舘大学}}|accessdate=2020-09-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917002952/https://www.kokushikan.ac.jp/tokyo2020/olympian.html|archivedate=2020-09-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

